Entahlah.

497
00:36:31,984 --> 00:36:33,485
Bagaimana sesimu dengan dr. Rush?

498
00:36:33,485 --> 00:36:34,903
Kau pasti akan suka.

499
00:36:35,821 --> 00:36:37,322
Dia berpihak padamu.

